
lutris : is game manager, handles native, Windows (via Wine/Proton), and emulated games. 


Disney's Aladdin    :   https://lutris.net/games/disneys-aladdin/


install games on separate drive(partition)
    create a directory(SteamLibrary) in the partition
    Open Lutris -> click on a game -> Configure
    Go to Game Options -> Set the install directory to /mnt/games/LutrisGames
    You can set a default in Lutris Settings -> Directories